    """

        """

        :rtype: bool

class SegmentTree:
    def __init__(self, n):
        self.n = n
        self.root = [i for i in range(n)]
        self.p = [i for i in range(n)]
        self.s = [None] * (n + 1)

    def add(self, i, x):
        self.root[i] = x
        self.p[i] = self.root[i]
        self.s[i] = x

    def subtree(self, i, x):
        self.p[i] = self.root[self.p[i]]
        self.s[self.s[i]] = self.root[i]
        return self.p[i]

    def add_to_p(self, i, x):
        self.p[i] = self.root[self.p[i]]
        self.s[self.s[i]] = self.root[i]
        return self.p[i]

    def add_to_s(self, i, x):
        self.s[i] = self.root[self.s[i]]
        self.p[i] = self.root[i]
        self.s[self.s[i]] = self.root[i]
        return self.s[i]

import sys
readline = sys.stdin.readline

N = int(readline())
A = list(map(int, readline().split()))
B = list(map(int, readline().split()))
C = list(map(int, readline().split()))

def sieve(x):
    if x not in A:
        return 0
    i = 0
    while i < N:
        j = i + 1
        while j < 50 and A[j] <= x:
            j += 1
        if j >= 50:
            i += 1
        i += 1
    return i

def solve(N, A, B):
    satisfaction = 0
    for i in A:
        satisfaction += solve(N-i, A, B)
    return satisfaction

Satisfaction = [0] + sorted(A, reverse=True)
for i in range(N):
    N_slice = A[i]
    A_slice = B[i]
    C_slice = C[i]
    C_slice_sum = 0
    for j in range(N):
        if j >= 50:
            j -= 1
        if j >= 50:
            j += 1
        j += 1
        j_slice = j + 1
        j_slice_sum += C_slice_sum
        C_slice_sum += C[j]
        C_slice_sum += C[j_slice]
        satisfaction += (j_slice + j_slice_sum)
    print(satisfaction)

import sys
readline = sys.stdin.readline

n,k = map(int,readline().split())
cracks = list(map(int,readline().split()))

def solve(c,k):
    nonlocal cracks
    nonlocal k
    if c == k:
        return abs(cracks[0] + cracks[1]) if k == 0 else 0
    elif c == k:
        return abs(cracks[0] - cracks[1]) if k == 0 else 0
    else:
        return abs(cracks[0] - cracks[1]) if k == 0 else 0

print((solve(c,k)))

    visited.add(x)
    for i in range(x):
        if A[i] < visited[x]:
            A[i] += visited[x]
        elif A[i] > visited[x]:
            A[i] -= visited[x]
            visited[x] = 0
    return visited
